Package: splittestr
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian and frequentist A/B split testing
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-08-12
Author: c(person("David", "Robinson", email = "drobinson@stackoverflow.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: David Robinson <drobinson@stackoverflow.com>
Description: Functions for Bayesian and frequentist A/B split testing. The
    main purpose of this package is to provide functions and support for a blog
    post about Bayesian A/B testing. It is not intended or documented to be used by
    others, though it can be.
